#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"- Update *Thunderbird* from 68.12 to [78.4.2](https://www.thunderbird.net/en-"
"US/thunderbird/78.4.2/releasenotes/)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  *Thunderbird* 78 replaces the *Enigmail* extension with built-in support for\n"
"  OpenPGP encryption.\n"
msgstr ""

