#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  If you used *Enigmail* before Tails 4.13, follow our [[instructions to\n"
"  migrate from *Enigmail* to *Thunderbird*\n"
"  78|doc/anonymous_internet/thunderbird/openpgp_migration]].\n"
msgstr ""

